name: UIPrinterPickerControllerDelegate
desc: A set of methods for managing the presentation and dismissal of a printer picker interface.

items.name: func printerPickerController(UIPrinterPickerController, shouldShow: UIPrinter) -> Bool
items.desc: Asks the delegate if the specified printer should be included in the picker.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerDidSelectPrinter(UIPrinterPickerController)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that a printer was selected.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerParentViewController(UIPrinterPickerController) -> UIViewController?
items.desc: Asks the delegate to provide the view controller to act as the parent of the printer picker.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerWillPresent(UIPrinterPickerController)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the printer picker is about to be displayed.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerDidPresent(UIPrinterPickerController)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the printer picker was displayed and is now visible.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerWillDismiss(UIPrinterPickerController)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the printer picker is about to be dismissed.

items.name: func printerPickerControllerDidDismiss(UIPrinterPickerController)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the printer picker was dismissed.
